This Privacy Policy (“Policy”) applies to WePartyapp.com, WeParty app and other WeParty-related sites, apps, communications and services (“Services”). WEJOY PTE. LTD. (hereinafter referred to as “WEJOY”, "we”, “us”, “our”) is the service provider and operator of WeParty and its Services. We fully respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it through our compliance with this Privacy and applicable laws and regulations. This Policy is meant to help you understand our practices related to the collection, use, storage, and disclosure of information we collect from or about you when you interact with us, your rights regarding the information provided to us, and how we safeguard your rights.
It is important to note that this Policy does not apply to any products, services, websites, or content that are offered by third parties (“Third Party Services”), which are governed by their respective privacy policies. We encourage you to read and review the privacy statements of each Third-Party Service that you may choose to use.
If you have any comments or queries about this Policy, or how we use your information, please contact us using the contact details provided below.
Please make sure to read this Policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your Personal Information and access it frequently to understand the updates to this Policy. If we update this Policy, we will notify you by announcements in the App or our website to let you know about the changes we made. By accessing or using our Services after we have placed such a notice, you are deemed to have accepted the updated Privacy Policy. You can check the “Effective Date” posted at the top of the Privacy Policy for the latest update time.
